Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reportNetStat(25.10)                                      reportNetStat(25.10)

Name
       reportNetStat

Syntax
       reportNetStat

       Reports statistical data of the design netlist such as number of cells,
       number of nets (including tri-nets and degen nets), number of pins, and
       number  of  IOs  in the design and number nets with different number of
       terms. The primitives used in the design are also listed.

       Example

                           Fri Apr 04 01:25:37 2025       reportNetStat(25.10)